#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_big_number
msgid "90%"
msgstr "90%"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_call_to_action
msgid "<b>50,000 people</b>, run Clean to grow their financial wealth."
msgstr ""
"<b>ປະຊາຊົນ 50,000 ຄົນ</b>, ນຳໃຊ້ Clean ເພື່ອສ້າງຄວາມຮັ່ງມີທາງດ້ານການເງິນຂອງພວກເຂົາ."

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"<br/>Providing reliable legal solutions tailored to your needs.<br/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>ສະໜອງທາງອອກທາງດ້ານກົດໝາຍທີ່ໜ້າເຊື່ອຖື ເຊິ່ງຖືກອອກແບບມາໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງທ່າ"
"ນ.<br/><br/>"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-fw fa-info-circle o_not-animable\" role=\"img\"/>  Trusted "
"expertise"
msgstr ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-fw fa-info-circle o_not-animable\" role=\"img\"/>  ຄວາມຊ່ຽວຊາ"
"ນທີ່ໜ້າເຊື່ອຖື"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_key_benefits
msgid ""
"Access specialized resources and expert insights that strengthen your case "
"and keep you informed on all legal matters."
msgstr ""
"ເຂົ້າເຖິງແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນສະເພາະດ້ານ ແລະ ຄວາມຮູ້ຈາກຜູ້ຊ່ຽວຊານທີ່ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຄະດີຂອງທ່ານມີນ້ຳໜັກ ແລະ ແຈ້ງໃຫ້ທ່ານຊ"
"າບກ່ຽວກັບທຸກບັນຫາທາງກົດໝາຍ."

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_features
msgid "All in one"
msgstr "ລວມທຸກຢ່າງໃນບ່ອນດຽວ"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_carousel
msgid ""
"At any moment, you may contact our advisor through the in-app video meeting "
"system."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດຕິດຕໍ່ທີ່ປຶກສາຂອງພວກເຮົາໄດ້ທຸກເວລາ ຜ່ານລະບົບການປະຊຸມວິດີໂອພາຍໃນແອັບ."

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_empowerment
msgid "Book an appointment"
msgstr "ຈອງນັດໝາຍ"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Business Strategy Consulting"
msgstr "ການໃຫ້ຄຳປຶກສາດ້ານກົນລະຍຸດທຸລະກິດ"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Cloud Computing Solutions"
msgstr "ທາງອອກດ້ານລະບົບຄລາວ"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Composed of 25 people from 25 to 66 years, we’re a young and dynamic "
"company. We have open positions, do not hesitate to contact us."
msgstr ""
"ປະກອບດ້ວຍບຸກຄະລາກອນ 25 ຄົນ ທີ່ມີອາຍຸຕັ້ງແຕ່ 25 ຫາ 66 ປີ, ພວກເຮົາແມ່ນບໍລິສັດຄົນຮຸ່ນໃໝ່ທີ່ມີຄວາມຄ່ອງຕົ"
"ວ. ພວກເຮົາມີຕຳແໜ່ງງານຫວ່າງ, ຢ່າລັງເລທີ່ຈະຕິດຕໍ່ຫາພວກເຮົາ."

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Comprehensive financial planning, including risk assessment, investment "
"strategy, and tax optimization for your business."
msgstr ""
"ການວາງແຜນການເງິນແບບຄົບວົງຈອນ, ລວມທັງການປະເມີນຄວາມສ່ຽງ, ກົນລະຍຸດການລົງທຶນ, ແລະ ການຄຸ້ມຄອງພ"
"າສີທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດສຳລັບທຸລະກິດຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Customized HR solutions, including talent acquisition, employee training, "
"and performance management to boost productivity."
msgstr ""
"ທາງອອກດ້ານການບໍລິຫານຊັບພະຍາກອນມະນຸດແບບປັບແຕ່ງສະເພາະ, ລວມທັງການສັນຫາບຸກຄະລາກອນ, ການຝຶກອົບຮົ"
"ມພະນັກງານ, ແລະ ການບໍລິຫານຜົນງານເພື່ອເພີ່ມສະມັດຖະພາບໃນການເຮັດວຽກ."

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_key_benefits
msgid "Customized Legal Strategies"
msgstr "ກົນລະຍຸດທາງກົດໝາຍແບບປັບແຕ່ງສະເພາະ"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_key_images
msgid "Customized solutions for your business needs"
msgstr "ທາງອອກທີ່ປັບແຕ່ງໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງທຸລະກິດທ່ານ"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Digital Marketing Services"
msgstr "ບໍລິການການຕະຫຼາດດີຈີຕອນ"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_key_images
msgid "Driving Success Through Innovation"
msgstr "ຂັບເຄື່ອນຄວາມສຳເລັດດ້ວຍນະວັດຕະກຳ"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_features
msgid "Easy to use"
msgstr "ນຳໃຊ້ງ່າຍ"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_carousel
